### Default state (2 users).
GET http://localhost:3006/api/users

### Switch to "empty".
POST http://localhost:3006/__mockr/scenario
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "empty" }

### Now empty.
GET http://localhost:3006/api/users

### Switch to "crowded".
POST http://localhost:3006/__mockr/scenario
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "crowded" }

### 12 users (2 baseline + 10 inserted).
GET http://localhost:3006/api/users

### Switch to "down" — every read returns 503.
POST http://localhost:3006/__mockr/scenario
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "down" }

### Now broken.
GET http://localhost:3006/api/users
